    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見プロ全国ツアー大阪公演前日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "さっき食べたたこ焼き、美味しかったね！\n東京で食べるたこ焼きとは、どこか違った気がする",
      "startTime": 6.6333335399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "関東のたこ焼きは、表面をカリッと揚げ焼きにしている\nお店が多いそうですね。関西は逆に、フワッと焼くとか",
      "startTime": 15.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "へ～、名前は同じなのに焼き方が違うんだ\nお好み焼きも違ったりするのかな？",
      "startTime": 25.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "さっき通ったお店で売ってたよね\nせっかくだし、食べに行こうかな！",
      "startTime": 31.4000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "いいですね～。こういう食べ歩きこそ遠征の\n醍醐味と言っても過言じゃないですよ",
      "startTime": 38.1333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよね！　{user}さん\nこの後のことについてなんですけど",
      "startTime": 44.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、すまない。伝えていなかったな\nそろそろホテルのチェックイン時間なんだ",
      "startTime": 49.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "移動の疲れもあるだろう\n明日も早いし、休める時にはゆっくり休んでおいてくれ",
      "startTime": 54.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……あ、そうですよね\n明日も早いですし……あはは……",
      "startTime": 62.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
